{"tid":491723,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"你講你對人一見鐘情/怦然心動嘅一刻,我將佢畫成幾格漫畫 [ 2 ]","createTime":"2017-12-06T20:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T04:26:39.000Z","uid":138632,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c8586f436ac6e690a0a69e8723d272df1dac8f34","tid":491723,"uid":138632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T20:19:23.000Z","msg":"之前個post鎖左推唔到所以開新<br />\n<br />\n舊 post : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/366169/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/366169/page/1</a><br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\nFrom : 點解廁所無廁紙<br />\n同佢瞹昧緊嗰陣一齊出過街 全程都大家都行得好近大家 係手臂貼住晒嗰隻 過馬路嗰陣佢無啦啦拖住左我 嗰刻個心勁緊張又好開心 個心跳得好快 好想問佢點解要拖住我但又驚問完佢會鬆手 之後搭巴士都一直無鬆到手 我捱係佢膊頭 就咁坐到落車 到依家都依然記得當時種心動 <br />\nBtw 已成ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/041853_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F041853_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=823fced7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/041856_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F041856_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=1f77f426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/041859_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F041859_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=a092124f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b41e75797bf375f1eb4e620216526005dc1a256","tid":491723,"uid":147677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12