ghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0b87a1ef279e156fb4b6e938d5dc5a172663af","tid":491723,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T23:16:42.000Z","msg":"樓主清舊po定接新單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc533a7ba6485a79eef7290e13f0a2ef368f0dd","tid":491723,"uid":138632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T23:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主清舊po定接新單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n由舊po開始揀啲有畫面啲嘅畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd62da2a2a7475fca898f3c027e9d77081ce120","tid":491723,"uid":138632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:50:16.000Z","msg":"From : 雪沙雪沙旋<br />\n<br />\n個陣係ocamp我地組坐埋一個圈黎玩 點知玩玩下有其他組圍埋黎一齊玩 我第一眼見到個男仔就覺得佢係我鍾意個type<br />\n之後到disco night 我真係冇注意到周圍 點知隊band一開始唱歌我發現個個男仔就企係我隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為個陣d人拋左好多個氣球出來 有一個差唔多飛到落我個頭到 佢幫我一手拍開左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然我地到宜家都唔識 但希望黎緊個sem可以識到佢 我係比較矮 佢係好高既 15x同18x <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/094950_5b1328822877b6099dd2bb46e8a1aa84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F094950_5b1328822877b6099dd2bb46e8a1aa84.jpg&h=f0092f41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/094957_3f93da36e4dcc70910e18ac429cf2a3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F094957_3f93da36e4dcc70910e18ac429cf2a3c.jpg&h=ac30b1a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7393bf523c727ac2491d1208825c6880fde23a3e","tid":491723,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:26:23.000Z","msg":"懂事以來冇試過一見鍾情，咁既情景畫唔畫到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60407b41658dcef92c9a398998f9048c4967dfe","tid":491723,"uid":84786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:03:38.000Z","msg":"佢155女 長髮 好瘦 已經一個人搬出尼住<br />\n嗰排考完dse 報緊大學<br />\n借D意上佢屋企叫佢教我面試技巧(佢話可以教我先嘅)<br />\n佢一開門 見到佢淨係著左件粉紅色Hollister長身oversize t shirt<br />\nbra又唔戴 啱啱醒咁樣<br />\n<br />\n我地之後坐左喺地下 盤膝坐*(見圖)<br />\n對腳撐開件T-shirt 根本就冚唔曬大髀<br />\n條底褲就露曬出尼 最仆街佢又要㩒件衫落去遮<br />\n但係件衫又會彈返上尼<br />\n<br />\n真係心動嗰下係 佢做自我介紹示範嗰下好自信 好認真 好性感<br />\n之後又叫佢教我soft skills 聽佢9up埋D歪理<br />\n就係好鐘意佢講野唔知醜嗰下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後自動做左兵...<br />\n<br />\n喺佢個角度應該就係:<br />\n考完試自己一個喺屋企 咁啱有條死毒撚癡埋尼<br />\n咪利用下囉 反正佢會買外賣上尼 又唔夠膽做D乜<br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔好畀我再見到佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/164846_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F164846_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=38d5637b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"563b76a7d4e68655f2dca48746b4f01a5029eba5","tid":491723,"uid":120494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:09:24.000Z","msg":"14年中文DSE，有個女仔遲到。<br />\n考完試之後撩佢吹水，之後一齊走<br />\n完"},{"pid":"57bdbc723aef5331e91adc14a7e1b5df80a46059","tid":491723,"uid":84786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:14:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一次見佢係帶佢隻猫去睇醫生，揸車去到佢樓下接佢，雪地景短褲高筒靴，佢抱住隻猫回眸一笑真係心動，長頭髪飄下咁，哥一下真係特別覺得佢靚又有愛心。<br />\n利申：係外國所以啲樓好矮</blockquote><br />\n鐘意小動物邊算有愛心...動物靠樣搵食架<br />\n如果佢樣衰D 係咪都會咁對佢先<br />\n如果對人都係咁先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efd39852c9bea390a5225ad4c689ee0fe6b27e3","tid":491723,"uid":84786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:16:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>14年中文DSE，有個女仔遲到。<br />\n考完試之後撩佢吹水，之後一齊走<br />\n完</blockquote><br />\n姓趙?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2fddbd6550142df2d05d0770baac3576a40bfbf","tid":491723,"uid":137863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:39:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"72891ed4d8dafd87112844a812763d8908e38705","tid":491723,"uid":138632,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T17:29:46.000Z","msg":"From : 告別の前<br />\n[url]<br />\n同一個男仔一齊去旅行個陣搭長途火車<br />\n然後我太眼瞓就挨住佢既膊頭咁瞓<br />\n瞓到中途我感覺到我個頭開始向前跌<br />\n然後佢好驚整醒我咁用另一隻手<br />\n慢慢擺返我個頭上去佢個膊頭度<br />\n佢一路都以為我仲瞓緊<br />\n但其實個陣我已經醒咗<br />\n仲有怦然心動既感覺<br />\n唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主[/url]<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/012928_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F012928_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=629dac26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/012929_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F012929_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=e969d8d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/012932_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F012932_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=e109f450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/012934_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F012934_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=54adc808&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d20eabf1afcd50963a89d62981de29f470b9ba90","tid":491723,"uid":162349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T20:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae621069c7ef5a5c21862462eb07fac4f747a34c","tid":491723,"uid":162349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T20:59:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講漏左個時我係18歲佢係16歲<br />\n唔該你啊樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a9ff6b8783f0f0559b8ee29abe1f6bce9e1ffa","tid":491723,"uid":127404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T21:05:56.000Z","msg":"繼續留名支持樓主<br />\n等咗你好耐"},{"pid":"95f102dc0f25a7b636eaaade49120a4b85125bba","tid":491723,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:36:23.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732528d225d7b1e720287d83fd26a5d7c02825c3","tid":491723,"uid":133501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:26:39.000Z","msg":"仲記得果個夜晚 凌晨時份<br />\n我地靜靜雞約出黎見<br />\n然後我地落左街係便利店門前傾計<br />\n講住我地之間先有既話題 <br />\n仲記得你我都講過 想同對方有將來<br />\n我仍然記得係暗淡既環境 光線打落你面上<br />\n你同我一齊開心既表情 <br />\n同埋經典既眼神<br />\n好似黑夜裡既 螢火蟲 令我心跳加速<br />\n至少有一刻相信 我搵到要搵既人 係你<br />\n所以如今 每到夜晚 我都特別記掛住你"}]}